Cloud watch - monitoring and observability service
why monitor - to check  performance / utilization / health / security


cloud watch collects logs, metrics , events and visualizes using automated dashboard.

metrics - data about performance of system. eg cpu utilization
events - something happening / change in resources - eg ec2 run to sttop
alarm - to trigger action based on metrics - cpu 80% utilization

CLOUD WATCH AGENT - To send notifications to cloud watch service
detail monitoring - monitoring every min
